author: Gamers Nexus
description:
Sponsor: Thermalright Frozen Prism 360 on Amazon - https://geni.us/FUqbQC
We talked to Scythe about the news of its European branch closing down, which the company says is for consolidation reasons (and that it is continuing to operate from the Taiwan branch). We also looked at the new Scycopter liquid cooler, Magoroku air cooler, Big Shuriken 4, and Shinkai prototype air cooler.

author: Gamers Nexus
description:
Sponsor: Thermaltake TR100 mini-ITX Travel Case on Amazon https://geni.us/Yn9DXb
Phanteks has a new T30-140 fan that required 6 years of engineering to make. We're joined by the company's CTO for a technical discussion about it. He talks misconceptions, "bigger number better" marketing, fan engineering, and manufacturing processes. We also cover the new G370A budget Phanteks case, th eXT M3, and the Evolv X2 Matrix.

Thanks to Bitwit for playing along. Find him here! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCftcLVz-jtPXoH3cWUUDwYw
